CONFUSION

Usage: ^gORDER <spirit> CONFUSION <target>^n

The confusion spirit power works the same as the confusion spell.
It causes the target to have their thoughts clouded, making it hard
to do even the most simple of tasks.

^WSee Also: ORDER^n

Also

Category: ^gILLUSION^n
Duration: ^gSUSTAINED^n

This spell causes the target to have debilitating hallucinations.
It causes the target to have problems doing even simple tasks.
The more successes rolled increases this difficulty up to a maximum
of the force of the spell.

Confusion only affects living targets.

^WSee Also: CAST, CHAOS^n
